  "text": "Analytics API Reference\nAnalytics API Reference\n\nWelcome to the Analytics API Reference. Select a product below to explore its Analytics API.\n\nAvailable Products​\nZscaler Analytics - Zscaler Analytics GraphQL API for analytics and reporting.\nAbout GraphQL​\n\nGraphQL is a query language for APIs that provides a complete and understandable description of the data in your API. It gives clients the power to ask for exactly what they need and nothing more.\n\nKey Benefits​\nPrecise Data Fetching: Request only the fields you need\nSingle Request: Get all required data in one API call\nStrong Typing: Schema defines exactly what's available\nIntrospection: Explore the API schema programmatically\nAuthentication​\n\nAll GraphQL endpoints require authentication. Include your bearer token in the Authorization header:\n\nAuthorization: Bearer YOUR_BEARER_TOKEN\n\nPrevious\nList All Reports\nNext\nOverview\nAvailable Products\nAbout GraphQL\nKey Benefits\nAuthentication",
